text: I made Nori crisps and they are divine! Another #experiment as I was craving salting crispy foods. The kids love them and it's a great way to get seaweed into your diet or to use to top salads with for crunch.  1 sheet of Nori Seaweed contains the same amount of omega-3 fatty acids as two avocados. This type of fat helps to raise healthy HDL cholesterol levels, while lowering harmful LDL cholesterol levels. Omega-3 fatty acids also help reduce inflammation in the body. Its high in natural Iodine so you can throw away that chemical table salt.  It aids digestion and seaweed is loaded with more calcium than broccoli and is almost as rich in proteins as legumes. Other nutrients in seaweed include vitamin B-12 and vitamin A so great for #vegans : I cut up 2 sheets into little squares and put them in a mixing bowl. I added 1 teaspoon of melted coconut oil and salt and pepper to taste. I then sprinkled about 1 teaspoon of water over them so they just soften and get coated by the seasoning but do not go soggy. I placed them in the dehydrator for 2 hrs on low but you could do it in the oven on low and watch them like kale chips. They are crispy salty and moorish so I will make them again and try other flavours like garlic powder and dried chilli or lemon juice instead of the water and white pepper.  If you have better will power than me you could store them in an air tight jar. #seaweedcrisps #raw #vegan #snacks #nori #iodine #fats #calcium #protein #omega3fattyacids #guthealth #healingfoods #gapsdiet #paleo #healthykidssnacks

Holland er mit nye yndlings land og helt specifikt Katwijk Surf Club!Til september skal Mads Emil og jeg skabe tang magi, sammen med en masse spændene og dygtige mennesker...Jeg har i 6 år været besat af tang og missionen med at få gjort det sexet, så det ikke kun er helsekost og heksedoktorer, som anvender det.Føler jeg er nået langt, men er ikke i mål.Der er kommer stadig flere og flere firmaer og personer som vil arbejde med tang, hvilket er pisse fedt. Jeg har selv lavet tv, tangkogebog, workshops og popup restaurant, alt sammen for at sætte fokus på havets miljø rigtige grøntsag.Til efteråret kommer der ny bog, lidt tv og en masse larm om tangen.Når jeg bliver inviteret til sådan et stort setup, som denne festival er, så bliver jeg oprigtigt glad og stolt, så tak Arie og Marco 🙏🏽Hvis du er i nærheden eller har brug for en over den kulinariske  oplever, så skynd dig at book en billet, det er så vanvittig inspirerede og dygtige mennesker du kan opleve i surf klubben!Jeg har indgået en aftale med @groovygraphic Som kommer til at lave en film omkring turen der ned, den kommer på youtube kanalen til efteråret.#KW106 #katwijksebrandingsurfclub #seamanseaweedchips #noplasticintheoceans #seaweedcrisps #trangtiltang#algenchips#futurefoods#tangchips#superfood#healthysnacks

text: BRINGING OUT THE SEA SPAGHETTI: that I harvested last summer. Delicious and crunchy it could be eaten as is like seaweed crisps! Sea spaghetti cooks up just like pasta especially if it is harvested young and it is great for grain free low carbohydrate meals as a bulk ingredient as you would use spaghetti pasta. It makes delicious carbonaras amongst other things. Simply rehydrate and use fresh on salads or boil as you would pasta. Sea spaghetti like its name suggests tastes more like pasta than it does seaweed!#grainfree #paleo #primal #lowcarb #nopasta #seaspaghetti #seaweed #glutenfree #wildfood #lovethewild #seaweedcrisps #ketodiet

As I promised, I’ll tell you a bit more about @abakusfoods seaweed crisps today! They come in three flavours: cheese, salt&vinegar and light salted 🧡💚💙 I was quite surprised with the fact that my favourite flavour was the cheese one! 🧀 The lightly salted ones would be good if you’re not feeling adventurous 😁 Salt&vinegar🧂crisps weren’t neither too salty nor to vinegar-y; I’d say that all the flavours were pretty good balanced! 👌 These crisps do taste a bit like seaweed but well, that’s what they are made out of! 😆 It’s not a really strong taste though, as the flavouring overshadows the taste of seaweed a bit. I really enjoyed these crisps, I’ve never heard of seaweed crisps before and I think this is a brilliant idea for crisps lovers...they’re rich in iodine and much lower in saturated fat and salt than regular crisps! You should definitely check out @abakusfoods and give seaweed crisps a go! 🌊 🌱 *Product gifted to me by Abakus Foods but this is my honest and impartial opinion!*••• #vegan #vegansofig #veganfoodshare #veganfood #whatveganseat #vegetarian #govegan #crueltyfree #eatclean #eatvegan #eathealthy #glutenfree #glutenfreevegan #plantbased #food #foodporn #weganizm #weganskie #weganskiejedzenie #vegansofpoland #cojedzaweganie #seaweed #crisps #seaweedcrisps #iodine #healthycrisps #cheese #saltandvinegar #veganuk #healthysnacks

text: .東京は☔️ですね🐸🌀.さて、日々2人の怪獣🦖に追われて、ずっと先延ばしにしていた#アイハーブ購入品 を記録✍️💗もう次の便が来ちゃうんだけどね😂.今回はいつものリピート品と食品かな.まず上の緑の袋から #SEAWEEDCRISPS 🍙これは、子供達のおやつにって思って買ったんだけど、少し食べてもう要らないって感じでした🙏ナッツが海苔に挟まれてるんだけど、うーんもう少し味付けしてもいいかなぁって💭.その左の#SAHALESNACKS は、アイハーブでもかなり人気商品で、ずーっと気になっててやっと購入したんだけど、はっきりいって私は好きじゃなかった🤣#メープル と#シナモン が強めなんだけど、甘すぎて‼️💧こってり濃厚な歯に挟まりそうな🦷甘みが好きな人は好きかもしれないんだけど、普段なるべく#白砂糖 を避けて生活してる私にはアウトな甘さでした〜🤣👍.そしてその下の#YUMEARTH 🧸🌈こちらも言わずと知れた大人気の#グミ 。小分けのパックになってるから、子供達と一袋づつ食べ過ぎなくていい感じ✌️日本の硬めのグミというより、グミみたいなゼリー❓#オーガニック のおやつにしてはとても美味しい🤤💗.その下の#ORGANICSTRAWBERRIES はもうだいぶ昔から何度もリピートしているもの🍓🍓オーガニックの苺を#フリーズドライ にしてあるんだけど、#宇宙食 って食べたことある？まさにあんな感じ！👽とっっても美味しくて子供達とエンドレスポリポリ👶#スムージー 作る時にそのままパパッと入れたり、#パンケーキ に入れても美味しいよ🥞💗.そして右上 #ネリーズランドリーソーダ の#洗濯洗剤 🧼基本的に、一般的に売られている【消臭】とか【除菌】って記載してる洗剤や石鹸は、少なからず皮膚や体に負担がかかります。我が家は子供が2人いるし、毎日使うものだから#ナチュラル なものを選びます🥰.#kidssoap は、子供達の#ボディシャンプー 🧴#バブルバス にもなるよ💗.そして#ヘリテージストア の#ローズウォーター 🌹これはもう一日中顔や体にシュッシュしてる必需品✨.#ミセスマイヤーズ の、手荒れ知らず#食器用洗剤 も、もはやストック無いと震える逸品👍.て感じかなぁ。.毎月頼んでるのにまだまだ試したいものだらけ💕.また記録します✍️😇.

text: Lime, Chilli & Coconut Seaweed Puffs by @shoreseaweed. They’re unique! Opening the pack I was hit by a waft of coconut. If you’ve ever taken the lid off a new jar of coconut oil, these had the same intense coconut aroma. They’re a deep golden brown & are speckled with flecks of real seaweed. They resemble Wotsits crisps to look at & have a similar open airy structure inside only with a firmer, crisper crunch. They taste nothing like Wotsits though. 😆. The coconut flavour hits you first followed by a citrusy, slightly bitter lime & a sweet yet also salty tang. The coconut seems to give them almost a cooling sensation in the mouth. I couldn’t taste the chilli at first but it creeps up on you after a few bites, becoming quite tongue tingling. Such a unique & intriguing mix of textures & flavours. My taste buds weren’t quite sure what was going on. I wasn’t sure I liked them at first, but they were so intriguing that I kept going back for more & soon I couldn’t stop eating them. 😋. I picked these up along with the Thai Chilli variety when I was ordering a few ingredients online from @superfood_market. I’ve always loved seaweed snacks but never seen it used in crisps before. It gives them a salty earthy umami kind of flavour. I can’t wait to try the Thai Chilli variety. Such a unique snack. They’re baked, not fried, made using real Scottish seaweed, GF & Vegan too.♥️#glutenfree #freefrom #newproduct #newfind #review #vegan #glutenfreevegan #dairyfree #seaweedcrisps #crisps #seaweedpuffs #snack #snacks #unique

Werbung Auf dem Blog stelle ich Euch einige Algenprodukte von KULAU vor. Die Produkte von Kulau sind zu 100 % biologisch, nachhaltig und köstlich.Ich erhielt zum Testen Organic Sea Spaghetti, welche zu 100 % aus Algen bestehen. Die Herkunft: biologischer Wildwuchs vor der Atlantikküste Spaniens.Man wäscht die Meeresalgen und weicht diese 30 Minuten in Wasser ein. Man kann sie als Pizza Belag oder als glutenfreie Pasta essen.Weiterhin erhielt ich Sweet Paprika. Es handelt sich hierbei um Bio-Algenchips. Diese sind auch glutenfrei. Zutaten sind hier: Meersalat, Paprika, Spinat, Grünkohl, Kokosblütenzucker, Kartoffelstärke und Rapsöl. Dann erhielt ich noch KULAU Bio-Nori-Snack Sea Salt. Hierbei handelt es sich zarte, knusprige Blätter, die auf der Zunge zergehen und einen milden Meeresgeschmack hinterlassen.Es gibt auch noch viele andere Produkte bei Kulau, welche aus Kokosnuss hergestellt werden.Kulau garantiert garantieren qualitativ hochwertige Produkte, die frei von künstlichen Zusätzen wie Aromastoffen, Ascorbinsäure und Farbstoffen sind und legen großen Wert auf nachhaltigen und zukunftsorientierten Handel und möchten dazu beitragen, nachfolgenden Generationen ein intaktes ökologisches, soziales und ökonomisches Gefüge zu hinterlassen.Schaut gerne einmal bei Kulau vorbei, die Auswahl ist hervorragend. Der Geschmack der Produkte ist sehr lecker und ich kann den Shop nur weiterempfehlen. text: Korean Snacks: You Must Try!1.	Orion Choco Pie (오리온 초코파이 | orion chokopai)They’re an integral part of Korean society, similar to a national symbol. The pronunciation is similar to how you’d say it in English, so it’s easy to say the title. Many Korean words are like this. 2.	Pepero White Cookie Sticks (빼빼로 화이트 쿠키)If you’re a fan of classic Pepero, you MUST try the Pepero white cookie sticks.3.	Chocolate Corns (초코콘) are pretty much a chocolate version of traditional cheese puffs.4.	Lotte’s Kancho Choco Biscuits (칸쵸 초코)There’s just a hint of milk chocolate inside so they’re not super rich, and they’re tiny enough that you can pop one (or six…) in your mouth and eat them on the go.5.	Dried Squid (해오징어 | haeojingeo)this delicious seafood snack is similar to beef jerky in texture and is utterly delicious if you enjoy squid in its other variations.6.	Lotte Ghana Milk Chocolate (가나 밀크 초콜릿)is one of the most popular brands of chocolate in Korea, and for good reason!7.	Pumpkin Monaca (호박모나카 | hobak monaka)Light and fluffy on the outside, these rice-based biscuits are filled with a thick and sweet pumpkin center. 8.	Custard Sweet Gold (카스타드 스위트 골드)has done it again with sweet gold, a sweet potato based custard treat that will leave you reaching for another as soon as you’re done.9.	Korean Sweet Cakes (찹쌀약과 | chapssal yakgwa)Light and flaky in texture, Korean sweet cakes are a great alternative to traditional cookies and candies if you’re in the mood for something quick and sweet.10.	Seaweed Crisps (김스낵)Well known for its superfood properties that make it full of nutrients, seaweed is incredibly versatile and can be incorporated into a huge variety of meals and snacks.#seoulbytes #korea #koreanfoods #koreanstreetfood #koreanfoodstyle #foodporn #foodlover #orionchocopie #pepero #peperowhitecookiesticks #chocolatecorns #lottekanchochocobiscuits #driedsquid #lotteghanamilkchocolate #pumpkinmonaca #curstardsweetgold #koreansweetscakes #seaweedcrispsCr: www.90daykorean.comStay tuned on our channel for more updates on Korean Snacks👉🏻 https://bit.ly/39WhxBw
